<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 20:10:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡因战争而试图推迟听证会，将于 12 月在腐败审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-december-after-an-attempt-to-delay-due-to-war/00000190-98d3-d590-affd-bad7c5840000</link><description>由于加沙战争和案件范围，内塔尼亚胡的律师要求推迟到2025年3月开始辩护证词。然而，法官强调公众利益需要迅速推进</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-december-after-an-attempt-to-delay-due-to-war/00000190-98d3-d590-affd-bad7c5840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长批准以色列国防军计划下个月向极端正统派人士发送征兵通知</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-approves-idf-plan-to-send-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-next-month/00000190-9865-d590-affd-ba755fed0000</link><description>国防部的声明没有具体说明将发送多少份征兵通知，但军方消息人士称将发送数千份。以色列国防军副参谋长表示，军队今年希望征召 4,800 名正统派男子，明年也将征召同样数量的士兵</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-chief-approves-idf-plan-to-send-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-next-month/00000190-9865-d590-affd-ba755fed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列戈兰高地遭火箭弹袭击，造成两人死亡；真主党声称对此次袭击负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/two-killed-in-rocket-strike-on-golan-heights-hezbollah-claims-responsibility-for-barrage/00000190-988a-d591-a7ff-fefa72c20000</link><description>大约 40 枚火箭弹射向戈兰高地，其中一枚击中了两人驾驶的汽车；该地区多处地点发生火灾；真主党表示，此次袭击是为了回应以色列在叙利亚针对一名关键特工的袭击事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/two-killed-in-rocket-strike-on-golan-heights-hezbollah-claims-responsibility-for-barrage/00000190-988a-d591-a7ff-fefa72c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令贝都因家庭向国家支付超过一百万谢克尔以支付驱逐费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-bedouin-family-to-pay-state-over-a-million-shekels-in-eviction-costs/00000190-978d-dfc0-a3f3-bffd333f0000</link><description>贝尔谢巴地方法院裁定，拒绝该州驱逐条款的四名贝都因家庭成员必须支付驱逐费用。他们辩称，国家不允许他们自行拆除房屋，而且规定的金额过高</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-bedouin-family-to-pay-state-over-a-million-shekels-in-eviction-costs/00000190-978d-dfc0-a3f3-bffd333f0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军发言人谈内塔尼亚胡及其政府如何落入哈马斯手中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</link><description>八个月来，前以色列国防军国际媒体发言人彼得·勒纳（Peter Lerner）从一个工作室到另一个工作室，试图让全世界相信以色列国防军在加沙行动的合法性。现在他说：“在国际舞台上，内塔尼亚胡和他的政府带领以色列失败了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-and-many-other-reservists-did-not-enlist-to-carry-out-a-nakba/00000190-916b-d0cb-abb9-f77b0e570000</guid></item><item><title>根据修订后的仇恨言论政策，Meta 将禁止针对“犹太复国主义者”的“非人化”帖子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/meta-to-ban-posts-targeting-zionists-with-dehumanizing-comparisons-to-jews-israelis/00000190-9854-d0d3-a5f3-98fc06bd0000</link><description>此举标志着这家科技巨头态度的转变，此前该公司认为“犹太复国主义者”一词仅在非常明确的情况下才代表犹太人。他们的声明中写道：“我们将删除使用反犹太主义刻板印象或威胁伤害的内容”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/meta-to-ban-posts-targeting-zionists-with-dehumanizing-comparisons-to-jews-israelis/00000190-9854-d0d3-a5f3-98fc06bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 277 天：红新月会表示其加沙城所有设施均已关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-277-red-crescent-says-all-its-gaza-city-facilities-have-shut-down/00000190-9835-d590-affd-ba35f9d80000</link><description>以色列人质丹妮拉·吉尔博亚 (Daniela Gilboa) 的家人批准出版哈马斯一月份发布的她被囚禁的视频 ■ 新一轮停战谈判定于周三在多哈举行 ■ 真主党发布以色列北部以色列国防军基地和军事基础设施的照片 ■ 据报道以色列杀人真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉的前保镖在贝鲁特-大马士革公路上罢工 ■ 战争进入 277 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-277-red-crescent-says-all-its-gaza-city-facilities-have-shut-down/00000190-9835-d590-affd-ba35f9d80000</guid></item><item><title>“不可接受”：马克龙在与内塔尼亚胡的通话中指责以色列部长干涉法国大选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-07-09/ty-article/macron-slams-israeli-ministers-interference-in-french-election-in-call-with-netanyahu/00000190-980a-d044-a997-d81e1f510000</link><description>选举前几天，马克龙警告内塔尼亚胡，侨民部长阿米猜·奇克利公开支持马琳·勒庞的极右翼国家集会党，构成对法国内政的不当干涉。以色列外交官称奇克利损害了与法国的关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-07-09/ty-article/macron-slams-israeli-ministers-interference-in-french-election-in-call-with-netanyahu/00000190-980a-d044-a997-d81e1f510000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟裂痕加深，利库德集团谴责本格维尔“不负责任的行为”并撤回议会法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/likud-blasts-ben-gvirs-irresponsible-behavior-pulls-bills-as-coalition-rift-deepens/00000190-97d5-d590-affd-b7d551470000</link><description>联合党鞭子奥菲尔·卡茨(Ofir Katz)表示，“我希望联合党帮助反对派伤害我们的情况能够停止。”他援引奥兹玛·耶胡迪特(Otzma Yehudit)的行为和主席本·格维尔(Ben-Gvir)拒绝支持部长级委员会批准的沙斯法案作为撤回所有计划的理由。议程上的法案</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:05:23 