0190-96ef-d8d3-adb9-deff2a800000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯10月7日袭击以色列7名加沙人，他们的命运不明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</link><description>在一张照片中，10 月 7 日遭到袭击的货车内有尸体。在另一张照片中，哈马斯恐怖分子从车里活捉了两人。除了尸体被送还给家人的司机外，九个月以来，以色列没有人知道其他加沙乘客的遭遇，直到上周</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-attacked-7-gazans-in-israel-on-october-7-their-fates-are-unknown/00000190-9684-dae0-a59d-96bc94d60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人头部被海绵头子弹击中，以色列赔偿10万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-pay-100k-in-damages-to-palestinian-shot-in-the-head-with-sponge-tipped-bullet/00000190-96b1-d1c5-a1d6-befd39260000</link><description>六年前，这名东耶路撒冷居民因海绵头子弹近距离射击而造成神经损伤，随后起诉该州。调查该事件的机构结案后达成和解，该男子的律师指控其妨碍司法公正</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-pay-100k-in-damages-to-palestinian-shot-in-the-head-with-sponge-tipped-bullet/00000190-96b1-d1c5-a1d6-befd39260000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸定居点关闭通往巴勒斯坦城镇的道路，激怒安全官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-settlement-closes-access-road-to-palestinian-town-angering-security-officials/00000190-968f-d1c5-a1d6-becfa1930000</link><description>阿里尔市市长封锁了道路，声称他正在帮助定居者的安全，但安全部门的消息人士建议市长“让军队和国防机构负责创造安全”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-settlement-closes-access-road-to-palestinian-town-angering-security-officials/00000190-968f-d1c5-a1d6-becfa1930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队预计将起诉虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-expected-to-indict-reservist-over-treatment-of-palestinian-detainees/00000190-964f-d1c5-a1d6-becf11900000</link><description>一名士兵据称殴打戴着手铐的巴勒斯坦被拘留者，以色列军法署预计将提出虐待指控。据巴勒斯坦报道，最近几天在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点附近发现了四名被拘留者，他们已经死亡并被戴上手铐。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-expected-to-indict-reservist-over-treatment-of-palestinian-detainees/00000190-964f-d1c5-a1d6-becf11900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉最高法院，必须尽一切努力将囚犯从斯德泰曼拘留中心清除</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-top-court-all-efforts-must-be-made-to-clear-prisoners-out-of-sde-teiman/00000190-9677-d1c5-a1d6-beff09b60000</link><description>据国家检察官办公室称，目前该设施内关押着 166 名被拘留者。该国宣布打算在六月之前将他们转移到以色列的其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 08:56:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-top-court-all-efforts-must-be-made-to-clear-prisoners-out-of-sde-teiman/00000190-9677-d1c5-a1d6-beff09b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对加沙休战发表评论后，美国和卡塔尔等待以色列的澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-qatar-waiting-for-israeli-clarifications-after-netanyahu-comments-on-gaza-talks/00000190-951b-d8d3-adb9-dddf39d40000</link><description>外国外交官表示，周三在卡塔尔与摩萨德主席大卫·巴尼亚的会晤将“至关重要”，因为调解人正在等待听取以色列是否根据内塔尼亚胡的“红线”文件提出任何弥合与哈马斯分歧的实际建议</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-qatar-waiting-for-israeli-clarifications-after-netanyahu-comments-on-gaza-talks/00000190-951b-d8d3-adb9-dddf39d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列购买芬兰反无人机系统以保护内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-purchased-foreign-